### ============================================================
### GROUP 4 — Subscription Limit Enforcement
### ============================================================

### Register a new trader (copy their ID from the response or DB)
POST {{hostAddress}}/api/identity/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testgroup4@traderforge.com",
  "password": "SuperSecretPassword123!"
}

###

### Login as trader — copy the returned token to @traderToken above
POST {{hostAddress}}/api/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testgroup4@traderforge.com",
  "password": "SuperSecretPassword123!"
}

###

### Get trader's current plan (shows limits: Basic = 2 strategies, 5 assets)
GET {{hostAddress}}/api/subscription/trader-plan
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

###

### Get active portfolio (returns the portfolio GUID for creating strategies/assets)
GET {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

###

### List all strategies for the authenticated trader (returns GUIDs)
GET {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio/strategies
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

###

### List all portfolio assets for the authenticated trader (returns GUIDs)
GET {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio/assets
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

###

### Create a strategy (portfolio resolved server-side from active portfolio)
POST {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio/strategies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

{
  "name": "My First Strategy"
}

###

### Activate/deactivate a strategy — replace id with the strategy GUID from GET
PUT {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio/strategies/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/state
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Add a portfolio asset (portfolio resolved server-side from active portfolio)
POST {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio/assets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.5,
  "entryPrice": 65000.00
}

###

### Remove a portfolio asset — replace id with the asset GUID
DELETE {{hostAddress}}/api/portfolio/assets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

###

### Change plan — now protected by downgrade check (P4)
### Create 2+ strategies first, then try to downgrade to Pro to test limit enforcement
POST {{hostAddress}}/api/subscription/change-plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: bearer {{traderToken}}

{
  "newPlanId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222"
}

###

